# ============================================================================
# MongoDB Native (User-space) - AMP Template Configuration
# ============================================================================
# This template installs MongoDB in user-space without requiring Docker or root.
# Downloads Debian-compatible MongoDB binary and runs it as the AMP user.
#
# Based on MySQL template approach: download binary, extract to user directory,
# initialize data directory, and run as user process.
# ============================================================================

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Template Identity and Metadata
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
